Class SimpleNestedTreeLifecycleProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.SimpleNestedTreeLifecycleProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LithoLifecycleListener, LithoLifecycleProvider

    public class SimpleNestedTreeLifecycleProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements LithoLifecycleProvider, LithoLifecycleListener
    LithoLifecycleProvider implementation that can be used to subscribe a nested ComponentTree to listen to state changes of the lifecycle provider that the parent ComponentTree is also subscribed to.
